{"word":"διαπειράομαι","slug":"διαπειράομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διαπειράομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>άσομαι</el>) (aor1 <el>-επειράθην</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-πεπείρᾱμαι</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to make trial</i> or <i>proof of, to have experience</i> of a thing, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/>"}]}